# =============================================================================
# GEMINI API CONFIGURATION (SERVER SIDE ONLY - NOT EXPOSED TO CLIENT)
# =============================================================================
#
# These API keys are ONLY read by Netlify Functions on the server.
# They will NEVER be injected into client side JavaScript bundles.
#
# You can add multiple keys for automatic rotation and rate limit handling:
# API_KEY_1=your-first-gemini-api-key
# API_KEY_2=your-second-gemini-api-key
# API_KEY_3=your-third-gemini-api-key
# ... up to API_KEY_20
#
# Single key fallback:
# API_KEY=your-single-gemini-api-key
#
# Note: Never commit actual API keys to version control!
# This file is just an example template.
#
# =============================================================================
# OTHER ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================================
#
# Add other environment variables below:
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
#
